author: Epic Games
description:
The next evolution of the award-winning skate™️ franchise is releasing in Early Access September 16th. Experience improved Flick-It controls, the rich physics based skateboarding gameplay that provides those “only in skate.™️“ moments and off-board exploration for full freedom in the online multiplayer world of San Vansterdam.

Your new favorite hangout awaits. 
Play for free* starting on September 16 on the Epic Games Store. Wishlist here: https://epic.gm/skate
title: skate. | Early Access Release Date Trailer

author: Epic Games
description: Chip 'n Clawz vs. The Brainioids is a 3rd person action game that seamlessly blends both action and real time strategy gameplay for a uniquely fun experience. Enjoy multiplayer mayhem with split screen couch co-op, 1 vs. 1 split screen, and online multiplayer to double the fun. https://epic.gm/chip-n-clawz
title: Chip 'n Clawz vs. The Brainioids | Launch Trailer

author: Epic Games
description: Today’s episode takes a closer look at the modular scenery customization and how park managers can tweak every aspect of their parks from the ground up. Jurassic World Evolution 3, launching 21 October and available to pre-purchase now on the Epic Games Store. https://epic.gm/jw-evolution
title: Jurassic World Evolution 3 | Building Your Parks
